OL,3,CRestaurant served food while plagued
OL,4,Cwith rat infestation - court hears
OL,6,FA restaurant in Newcastle continued to
OL,7,Fserve food despite being plagued with
OL,8,Fa major infestation of rats, a court
OL,9,Fhas heard.
OL,11,FWhen Environmental Health Officers
OL,12,Finspected TeAmo Chinese and BBQ House,
OL,13,Fon Percy Street, they found piles of
OL,14,Fsoil on the kitchen floor ` evidence
OL,15,Fthat rodents had burrowed through the
OL,16,Frestaurant's structure.
OL,18,FRat droppings were found throughout
OL,19,Fthe restaurant, on work surfaces,
OL,20,Funder the oven and the sink used for
OL,21,Fwashing pans.
