OL,3,CRestaurant served food while plagued
OL,4,Cwith rat infestation - court hears
OL,6,FA rat carcass was found on the kitchen
OL,7,Ffloor at a subsequent inspection
OL,8,Ffollowing extensive pest control
OL,9,Ftreatment as well as other breaches of
OL,10,Ffood safety legislation.
OL,12,FFood business operator Min Hou, of
OL,13,FSpring Garden Lane, Newcastle,
OL,14,Fadmitted five breaches of food hygiene
OL,15,Fregulations when she appeared before
OL,16,FNewcastle Magistrates. She was fined
OL,17,F#533, ordered to pay a victim
OL,18,Fsurcharge of #213 and #1,200 costs
OL,19,Fmaking a total of #1,946.
