OL,6,FThe company Tea and More Limited, of
OL,7,Fwhich Hou was a director, also
OL,8,Fadmitted the same five offences. It
OL,9,Fwas fined #8,000, ordered to pay a
OL,10,Fvictim surcharge of #2,000 and #1,200
OL,11,Fin costs making a total of #11,200.
OL,13,FThe court on Friday 5 July heard the
OL,14,Frestaurant previously had a five-star
OL,15,Fhygiene rating when the council
OL,16,Freceived a complaint.
