OL,3,CRestaurant served food while plagued
OL,4,Cwith rat infestation - court hears
OL,6,FEnvironmental Health Officers who
OL,7,Finspected the premises in April 2023
OL,8,Fimmediately discovered it had a rat
OL,9,Finfestation. The kitchen was dirty and
OL,10,Fgreasy and there was soil on the floor
OL,11,Fcaused by rats burrowing into the
OL,12,Fkitchen.
OL,14,FThere were smudge marks along the
OL,15,Fskirting boards where the rats had
OL,16,Fbeen running and there was evidence
OL,17,Fstaff had continued to prepare food in
OL,18,Fthe dirty kitchen.
