OL,3,CRestaurant served food while plagued
OL,4,Cwith rat infestation - court hears
OL,6,FBehind a piece of cardboard and the
OL,7,Flid of a deep fat fryer was a large
OL,8,Frat hole stuffed with six wax blocks
OL,9,Fof poison. The infestation was
OL,10,Fdescribed as prolonged and well
OL,11,Festablished.
OL,13,FWhen approached by officers, Hou
OL,14,Fvoluntarily closed the restaurant
OL,15,Fimmediately and was told to eradicate
OL,16,Fthe infestation and then deep clean
OL,17,Fthe entire premises before officers
OL,18,Fwould consider allowing the premises
OL,19,Fto reopen.
