OL,3,CRestaurant served food while plagued
OL,4,Cwith rat infestation - court hears
OL,6,FShe called in a pest control expert
OL,7,Fwho initially believed the rats were
OL,8,Fcoming from the sewers below the
OL,9,Fproperty. When officers returned weeks
OL,10,Flater, they discovered cleaning
OL,11,Fstandards remained poor. Rat droppings
OL,12,Fwere found on a shelf and in a box
OL,13,Fstoring chopping boards.
OL,15,FIn July 2023 the restaurant was given
OL,16,Fa one-star hygiene rating and Hou was
OL,17,Finterviewed under caution with a view
OL,18,Fto taking formal action.
OL,20,FThe business has now been dissolved.
