OL,4,Cwith rat infestation - court hears
OL,6,FNewcastle City Council's Cabinet
OL,7,Fmember for a resilient city, Cllr Irim
OL,8,FAli, said: "This is an horrific breach
OL,9,Fof food hygiene regulations. No one
OL,10,Fcould fail to be disgusted at the
OL,11,Fcondition of that restaurant. I am
OL,12,Fjust relieved it has now closed and no
OL,13,Fone has been poisoned.
