OL,6,F"I would like to pay tribute to our
OL,7,FFood Safety Team for the important job
OL,8,Fthat they do keeping the public safe.
OL,9,FI hope the penalties handed out in
OL,10,Fthis case act as a reminder to all
OL,11,Ffood businesses to ensure their
OL,12,Fpremises are pristine and that they
OL,13,Fact as soon as they discover a problem.
OL,15,F"When people eat out, they rightly
OL,16,Fexpect the highest food hygiene
OL,17,Fstandards.
OL,19,F"As a council we will not hesitate to
OL,20,Ftake enforcement action when
OL,21,Fregulations are breached."
